rows.label: qev086005_MSG0013
rows.name:
Looks like you haven't found those materials yet.
I guess some of 'em are pretty rare.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086005_MSG0012
rows.name:
Energy tubes especially. You have to take on tough
hostiles like those pawn puges in the Seaswept Base
if you want to get your hands on one.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086005_MSG0011
rows.name:
I know it won't be easy to gather them all,
but we're counting on you here. Good luck.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086005_MSG0001
rows.name:
You really got 'em all? Wow.
I guess everything I heard about you guys is true![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086005_MSG0002
rows.name:
These will mean a nice boost in
our manufacturing quality, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086005_MSG0003
rows.name:
Absolutely! Now we'll never have to
hunt for old parts again.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086005_MSG0005
rows.name:
Slowly but surely, we're building
a sustainable future for ourselves on this planet...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086005_MSG0006
rows.name: And it's all thanks to the dedication of people like you, Lin.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086005_MSG0007
rows.name:
With the support of some very
patient indigenous peoples, of course.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086005_MSG0009
rows.name:
All right, now it's time to build a
sustainable future for Tatsu's stomach.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086005_MSG0010
rows.name:
Oh-ho-hoooo! Linly put spring into Tatsu step!
Dance of sustainable joy![ST:wait ]
